{"tid":690752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今屆世界盃12個小知識","createTime":"2018-06-05T06:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T16:55:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":191,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7d8a7580808b4da3e5ebe744eb309b71c8d04b","tid":690752,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511115/org/98e54294b2ea122b6c17ee38119d3102.jpg/Ure4zwcV5U8InyboXEdStpidp6Sq_vmkaOV5EmjleRI?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511115%2Forg%2F98e54294b2ea122b6c17ee38119d3102.jpg%2FUre4zwcV5U8InyboXEdStpidp6Sq_vmkaOV5EmjleRI%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=4032d755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n45歲的埃及<span style=\"color: red;\">廢老</span>門將艾哈達里（Essam El-Hadary）是今屆736名球員中年紀最大的一位，他在1973年1月15日出世，如果上陣的話將刷新世界盃紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511116/org/a3db62acab7de210fb6d6724ef6e319b.jpg/oJn_rM3NVqxJ48ojxqSCLKsUlvIY7ArFo1B8NKNQfDQ?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511116%2Forg%2Fa3db62acab7de210fb6d6724ef6e319b.jpg%2FoJn_rM3NVqxJ48ojxqSCLKsUlvIY7ArFo1B8NKNQfDQ%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=5abf5a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19歲的澳洲中場丹尼爾阿辛尼（Daniel Arzani）是今屆最年輕的球員，也是唯一一名在1999年出生的球員，他生於1999年1月4日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511119/org/f455204bb5660c8cae07758749e347a4.jpg/D-o-a0wh4qgC0Dlj2Z0GVl72SwKPUp57GrDjoxqw46M?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511119%2Forg%2Ff455204bb5660c8cae07758749e347a4.jpg%2FD-o-a0wh4qgC0Dlj2Z0GVl72SwKPUp57GrDjoxqw46M%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=234c9746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最多球員在1992年出世，在736名球員中有85位，佔12%，這些球員現25至26歲，例如尼馬；之後最多球員出生的一年是1990年，有71位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511124/org/efc47c8a18bfa6e87a6b4d1b7b0a1a67.jpg/muvN_9VucXeUgUX82yEHyRf-9WQ_k1lu45cSWuOXElo?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511124%2Forg%2Fefc47c8a18bfa6e87a6b4d1b7b0a1a67.jpg%2FmuvN_9VucXeUgUX82yEHyRf-9WQ_k1lu45cSWuOXElo%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=9bc22a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最高的球員是克羅地亞門將路維卡連歷（Lovre Kalinić），這名效力真特的28歲球員身高2.01米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511117/org/fa832f58374828ec2e4a56f476aa22c3.jpg/oVZdlp9oMJlqxahzCELoGY9Wu7kYwBCRgpqizIKaosw?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511117%2Forg%2Ffa832f58374828ec2e4a56f476aa22c3.jpg%2FoVZdlp9oMJlqxahzCELoGY9Wu7kYwBCRgpqizIKaosw%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=45d6a228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最高的非門將球員是丹麥後衛維斯達加特（Jannik Vestergaard），這名效力慕遜加柏的25歲球員身高2米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511118/org/aa1c92cd5957bddedd21a5f13d731cda.jpg/43fak93BaD0jbPrLo2l6BYzqVktPtMTSOtk0azrZNGs?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511118%2Forg%2Faa1c92cd5957bddedd21a5f13d731cda.jpg%2F43fak93BaD0jbPrLo2l6BYzqVktPtMTSOtk0azrZNGs%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=26ef3e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最矮的球員有3位，他們同樣身高1.65米，分別是巴拿馬中場艾拔圖昆特路（Alberto Quintero）、沙特阿拉伯中場耶耶艾舒歷（Yahya Al-Shehri）及瑞士中場梳頓<span style=\"color: red;\">沙基利</span>（Xherdan Shaqiri）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511121/org/92d04630c3f3a46f17211fbe658d7170.jpg/3zyXMpeBImLkYn1pO_ukw1Y2pGUWQiccxsxNtcbMTbU?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511121%2Forg%2F92d04630c3f3a46f17211fbe658d7170.jpg%2F3zyXMpeBImLkYn1pO_ukw1Y2pGUWQiccxsxNtcbMTbU%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=a4d9ccc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最多球員來自英格蘭球會，在736名球員中，有124位在英格蘭落班，佔17%，包括比利時的奇雲迪布尼；緊隨其後的有西班牙球會（81名）、德國球會（67名）、意大利球會（58名）及法國球會（49名）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511120/org/02bcdf4eaed86c579a3ad66346ab5de6.jpg/XTaSpcy_Gkx93wUeUJyfjifQsYP0Im49JfOkbSXzpG0?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511120%2Forg%2F02bcdf4eaed86c579a3ad66346ab5de6.jpg%2FXTaSpcy_Gkx93wUeUJyfjifQsYP0Im49JfOkbSXzpG0%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=4590becb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英格蘭是今屆唯一一支全部23人都來自本國聯賽的球隊，而<span style=\"color: red;\">塞內加爾及瑞典</span>則沒有國腳效力本國聯賽球隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511122/org/ab25f10e7047dcc15e6fd073defd45cf.jpg/rWg8RfGaIHxKycKdrcYwqcXc8nbs-MuW_nonR_56J0c?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511122%2Forg%2Fab25f10e7047dcc15e6fd073defd45cf.jpg%2FrWg8RfGaIHxKycKdrcYwqcXc8nbs-MuW_nonR_56J0c%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=6582f788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆有14名巴塞隆拿球員參加世界盃，他們分屬9支國家隊，分佈於8組。換言之，今屆每組都有巴塞球員，例如A組有蘇亞雷斯而H組有耶利文拿，至於G組則有華美倫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511125/org/9a39210dc088ccd0eb0a6277a23ef259.jpg/9T4h-_FZyB4blw3LabDIj6e-6ciVopbC0fJN79HyTe8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511125%2Forg%2F9a39210dc088ccd0eb0a6277a23ef259.jpg%2F9T4h-_FZyB4blw3LabDIj6e-6ciVopbC0fJN79HyTe8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=0df44fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，巴塞並非最多球員入選的球會，英超的曼城有16人入選，包括巴西的加比爾捷西斯，而應屆歐聯冠軍皇家馬德里亦有15人入選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511123/org/afc28bb52c4641b487ef7d913cc4d5f9.jpg/-Piinj6wZEHIc6FGUe7gsTcjp-yvmdxyTrq3EU66txE?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511123%2Forg%2Fafc28bb52c4641b487ef7d913cc4d5f9.jpg%2F-Piinj6wZEHIc6FGUe7gsTcjp-yvmdxyTrq3EU66txE%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=b9278507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最多球員在2月出生，有81人，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">賤種朗拿度</span>；3月及1月僅緊其後，分別有75人及74人在這兩個月出世，而4月亦有72人出世，可見今屆的球員集中在年初出世。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1511126/org/fe4a1b38bade0ef4c314d89552794ff3.jpg/1SQzl_u-fxiXXqNYq4QZ5hHO9VlG04Up9U3Pp_VNz6c?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1511126%2Forg%2Ffe4a1b38bade0ef4c314d89552794ff3.jpg%2F1SQzl_u-fxiXXqNYq4QZ5hHO9VlG04Up9U3Pp_VNz6c%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=63354252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆最少球員在11月出世，只有35人，包括保羅戴巴拿、費蘭尼及卡斯柏舒米高，第二少的是12月，有43人，例如希古恩。"},{"pid":"aa0c8b59a8874fb010dc23096035364cb40abc2f","tid":690752,"uid":165978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8af067b6b983b75b77cd85b3fc6114dd61c45e","tid":690752,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbc4771700f890f38193f92c783eebaed2c5ac5","tid":690752,"uid":34572,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"沙基利死矮仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55582002c7259120dbb3acaf6956a5417d072506","tid":690752,"uid":57035,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"話肥哨賤種<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mrrm.com.hk/uploads/images/Transformation/Cheung%202A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrrm.com.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2FTransformation%2FCheung%25202A.jpg&h=0ef65f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b98d8c58a4f9190726490e567b210cf9bb5d6b4","tid":690752,"uid":133100,"like":21,"dislike":52,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"負皮係俾你句賤種朗拿度"},{"pid":"7aff7b0f7a3c47c6f080be28543e115644808848","tid":690752,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"55582002c7259120dbb3acaf6956a5417d072506","tid":690752,"uid":57035,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"話肥哨賤種<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mrrm.com.hk/uploads/images/Transformation/Cheung%202A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrrm.com.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2FTransformation%2FCheung%25202A.jpg&h=0ef65f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"腦殘? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbcc7230a860e0c22206edd8f6e8f7bd5b64df2","tid":690752,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"王生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b2a7b08afe5bd97c8507b13984e6147239f150","tid":690752,"uid":165817,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"無啦啦話人廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e13917221d025557037129e44cd46498f717c4","tid":690752,"uid":404,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"丹麥個中堅係又高又勁重  成98kg"},{"pid":"f70d55adbf4eda40b8652aafabc01209047a70bd","tid":690752,"uid":54373,"like":62,"dislike":9,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"f7b2a7b08afe5bd97c8507b13984e6147239f150","tid":690752,"uid":165817,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"無啦啦話人廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:34:27.000Z","msg":"保方40歲已經比賤種話廢老<br />\n<br />\n45歲簡直人瑞啦"},{"pid":"c13a167e560ffcc3fdf46db121406491268ab4bb","tid":690752,"uid":404,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"英格蘭是今屆唯一一支全部23人都來自本國聯賽的球隊<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野本來發生係其他國家係好<br />\n<br />\n但英格蘭就相反"},{"pid":"fe6dca669b3aca740a2954af3bb25ec7c9c90563","tid":690752,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"C朗第一!!!