mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946e8b9fb34d785855c9dfd808399515bc37ff13","tid":690752,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"搵到重點了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b83e4037d48459b5d037054ecb1112f84d08cfd","tid":690752,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"英撚又可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0ec374ccc8af2ea612cced69f47c29d1ea3257","tid":690752,"uid":4618,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"最後一屆無00後嘅世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91838d61065ee1443b86ce9b841755ae7289881","tid":690752,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"【香港隊U23初選名單！】&mdash; 第十八屆亞洲運動會<br />\n<br />\n第十八屆亞洲運動會將於本年八月中，<span style=\"color: red;\">喺</span>印尼雅加達舉行，<span style=\"color: red;\">現在</span>公佈40人初選名單（包括3名超齡球員），入選球員如下：<br />\n<br />\n守門員：陳嘉豪、李溢晉、謝家榮、王子聰、袁皓俊<br />\n<br />\n後衛：陳港斌、羅振庭、列斯奧*、羅梓駿、劉學銘、韋健豪、謝朗軒、徐宏傑、勞烈斯、姚浩明、余沛康、余煒廉<br />\n<br />\n中場：陳柏熹、鄭俊彥、黎厚希、林衍廷、林嘉緯*、羅曉聰、顏卓彬、周緣德、杜國榆、蕭俊銘、陳俊樂、黃駿軒、胡晉銘、茹子楠<br />\n<br />\n前鋒：鄭兆均、鄭展龍、趙少維、鍾偉強、播磨浩謙、佐迪*、黎洛賢、林樂勤、安永佳 <br />\n<br />\n*為超齡球員<br />\n<br />\n#撐自己人 #香港勁揪 #第十八屆亞洲運動會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb3a81afad133480eeaea0a557092d378c16495","tid":690752,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a91838d61065ee1443b86ce9b841755ae7289881","tid":690752,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-